    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "HelixCare AI Governance & Reliability Operations",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### HelixCare AI Governance & Reliability Operations\nLive runtime telemetry from Agent API, LLM Gateway, Guardrails, Approval Workflow, Prometheus, and Grafana. This view proves governed AI execution, fallback routing, human review controls, incident containment, and platform SLO monitoring in real time."
