        "content": "| Control Objective | Current Evidence | Operational State |\n|---|---:|---|\n| Unsafe outputs delivered | 0 | Contained before delivery |\n| Guardrail policy enforcement | Active | Clinical, PHI, prompt-injection checks running |\n| Provider resilience | Active fallback route | Primary degradation routed automatically |\n| Human review workflow | Queue monitored | High-risk requests staged for approval |\n| Observability coverage | Prometheus targets healthy | Agent API + LLM Gateway scraping live |"
